      "text": [
        "1129 - وَقَالَ اَلصَّادِقُ عَلَيْهِ اَلسَّلاَمُ: «أَذِّنْ خَلْفَ مَنْ قَرَأْتَ خَلْفَهُ."
      ],
      "translations": {
        "en.bab-ul-qaim-publications": [
          "Hadith.1129 - Imam Jafar ibn Muhammad Al-Sadiq (as) said:\n\"Give the call to prayer (adhan) behind the one you recited the prayer behind”."
        ]
      }
    }
